            <title>[SOLR-15280] Misleading error message in HdfsDirectoryFactory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15280</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the &lt;tt&gt;size(String path)&lt;/tt&gt; method of&#160;HdfsDirectoryFactory the error messages contain the &quot;Error checking if hdfs path exists&quot; text, which is probably a block-copy error from the &lt;tt&gt;exists(String path)&lt;/tt&gt; method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
